{"tid":1076701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯兩軍用飛機降委內瑞拉加強兩國聯繋","createTime":"2019-03-25T05:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T00:02:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65b2f51ce0eb5867f1b86b42d53348811e8ae09e","tid":1076701,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯兩軍用飛機降委內瑞拉加強兩國聯繋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190325022144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190325022144&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6VGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=d25c392e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190325022144</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯兩架空軍飛機載著一名國防官員和近100個士兵, 及一批物資, 星期六降落委內瑞拉的主要機場, 突顯委內瑞拉加強與俄羅斯的聯繫.<br />\n<br />\n        據報其中一架飛機載著俄羅斯地面部隊參謀長, 另一架貨機載著35公噸物資. 貨機已在星期日下午離開加拉加斯. 委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅上星期三曾表示, 俄羅斯會為委內瑞拉提供藥物. 俄羅斯在2月曾將300公噸人道援助物資送到委內瑞拉. 去年12月, 兩架可以攜帶核武器的俄羅斯戰略轟炸機降落委內瑞拉, 展示對馬杜羅政府的支持, 俄羅斯曾派出部隊到委內瑞拉舉行聯合軍事演習. 美國形容俄羅斯的舉動是侵犯美洲地區."},{"pid":"f934db497f86200fd4bb2a054d83ba8bab1f2e50","tid":1076701,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"又搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己都窮到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75732bdd3e622e649f035f8f069ce299383fa615","tid":1076701,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"死俄撚同支那世界兩大毒瘤 全球有共識唔撐佢地就撐到行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6186a642fdebe2402d370659030a8b71e0e2c3","tid":1076701,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"100名士兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd140c56190e952b96d3e388c7803e31f0b03fad","tid":1076701,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco